<% content_for :title, "SMS Program – StillOn" %>

<div class="sms-page">
  <div class="sms-shell">

    <div class="sms-header">
      <h1>StillOn SMS Program</h1>
      <p>StillOn sends SMS reminders to help friend groups stay coordinated around recurring hangouts.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="sms-section">
      <h2>How opt-in works</h2>
      <p>There are two ways someone opts in to receive SMS messages from StillOn:</p>

      <div class="sms-optin-block">
        <h3>1. Organizer signup</h3>
        <p>When an organizer creates their account, they enter their phone number to receive a verification code. The following consent language is shown before they submit:</p>
        <div class="sms-consent-example">
          By continuing, you agree to receive SMS messages from StillOn, including a verification code and event reminders. Msg &amp; data rates may apply. Reply STOP to opt out.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sms-optin-block">
        <h3>2. Guest RSVP</h3>
        <p>Guests receive an invite link shared by the organizer. When they open the RSVP page, they may optionally enter their phone number to receive a day-of reminder. The following consent language is shown inline with the phone field:</p>
        <div class="sms-consent-example">
          We'll send you one SMS the morning of the event. Msg &amp; data rates may apply. Reply STOP to opt out.
        </div>
        <p class="sms-note">Phone number is always optional. Guests who do not provide a number are never sent SMS.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sms-section">
      <h2>Message types</h2>
      <ul class="sms-list">
        <li><strong>Verification code</strong> — sent once when an organizer enters their phone number during signup.</li>
        <li><strong>RSVP reminder</strong> — sent 2 days before a scheduled hangout: <em>"Still on for [Event] on [Date]? RSVP here: [link]"</em></li>
        <li><strong>Event reminder</strong> — sent the morning of a hangout to confirmed attendees who opted in at RSVP time.</li>
        <li><strong>Cancellation notice</strong> — sent the morning of a hangout if it has been cancelled.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="sms-section">
      <h2>Opt-out &amp; support</h2>
      <ul class="sms-list">
        <li>Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to unsubscribe from all StillOn SMS messages.</li>
        <li>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for support information.</li>
        <li>Message and data rates may apply.</li>
        <li>Message frequency varies based on your group's hangout schedule.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
